/** * Author(s) of this code: * * Joven Manikiza */ import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { Table, Link, Heading, Main, SectionBreak, Pagination } from 'govuk-react'; import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; import Navigation from '../../Components/Navigation'; const db = new sqlite3.Database('LocalDatabase.db'); function Profile() { const navigate = useNavigate(); const [data, setData] = useState({}); useEffect(() => { db.all('SELECT * FROM patients WHERE NHSNumber = ?', [1234567890], (err, rows) => { if (err) { console.error(err.message); } setData(rows[0]); }); }, []); return (
navigate("/Patient")} previousPage> Back to start navigate("/GPServices")} nextPage> GP Services Profile Name {data.fullName} navigate("/NameChangeStart")} children="Change"/> D.O.B {data.dob} navigate("/DOBChangeStart")} children="Change"/> Gender {data.gender} navigate("/GenderChangeStart")} children="Change"/> Address {data.address} navigate("/AddressChangeStart")} children="Change"/> Email {data.email} navigate("/EmailChangeStart")} children="Change"/> Contact No. {data.contact} navigate("/NumberChangeStart")} children="Change"/> Password ************* navigate("/PasswordChangeStart")} children="Change"/>
); } export default Profile;
